    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising BMW E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This vehicle exhibits exceptional mechanical health, with the high-pressure VANOS system fully serviced and the rear subframe reinforced for long-term structural integrity. The powertrain benefits from individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering an unfiltered, high-revving analog experience. The chassis remains taut, utilizing factory-spec dampers and bushings to preserve its legendary steering feedback and lateral composure. This is a turnkey, collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
